data.title: Margaret Mary O'Brien Taylor (1865
data.meta_description: Daughter of John O'Brien and Catherine Taylor  Mother of Sr. Marie Celine, S.S.J. (Helen); Ann V. Taylor (d. 10/22/1995 Lansdale, Pa); Joseph A. Taylor (d. 6/6/1988); Sr. Mary Virgine, S.S.J.(Margaret); John J. Taylor (D. 6/7/1967); Martin Taylor (d. 1/3/1968 Phila)  Brother of Michael O'Brien (d. 5/25/1934...
